{"h955cfd16g2de7g4075gbc3dg0a8a55e7ad1d": ["*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "f9d5f108-14ed-409f-88c3-2bb78f3c17fc"], "hc63b8826ge443g40b1ga057ga7e353e6ce88": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "cccc3e68-a0bc-4594-a335-24413d511448"], "ha75fb2cfg34e2g418aga1c5g24cc0558ed80": ["*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "d92487f5-803b-4037-b0ec-fa36d7ac38e7"], "h95549433g37adg4599ga259gaf1ac08e7434": ["Who are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "970387f1-58ea-441f-838b-87f403be5ef3"], "h24ac5946ge7f3g4fa5gaeedg5a9a5eb96717": ["Alfira... apprentice... bard...", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "de0505f7-5107-4fd8-9254-c6663ddd06e9"], "h4339e45dg8ce5g4f7cg84d8gec245605231d": ["Where were you going?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "707f663c-0637-560b-b2a3-65ab350395bb"], "h23bf0d12g985cg45d8g837eg8f47ef20ae1c": ["Elfsong Tavern... Baldur's Gate...", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "e4d5dbd8-8d63-8d64-656f-8dff65f07392"], "hc119d73egd403g4b7eg98cfgc416fe1847c0": ["Why the Elfsong Tavern?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "8c1ac0f2-f884-9b06-514e-c6dff6ae4de8"], "h66913a6cgf12dg4d33gb54fg97b6e3bb6ccf": ["To perform there... to sing... for Lihala...", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "e63e54fb-454a-993c-6706-c945ea95d3d4"], "h5a08afc2g559fg4196g9069g00378fddd094": ["Did you come here alone?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "8bbaa962-a439-aa50-f96a-aa23a9fc463e"], "h32b9258agb77cg4475g86b5gd8637a1a7324": ["With... Lihala... but... but...", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "34419180-c562-c2a3-cbda-50c773bb6148"], "heb23b70fg9438g4610gbbd5g506e46021a90": ["Who is Lihala?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "14c05293-2b74-032d-c8de-1553105ea9b2"], "h29aec427gd7bfg4d4ag945fg68408310da29": ["Teacher... friend... everything to me. But gnolls... ripped her... apart...", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "de452f3a-24fc-3ad6-51cf-8752e6db74fa"], "h7e8397c7gd7ccg4370gbb4bg31a953ee41e5": ["You met gnolls? How did you survive?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "8ad0aef3-3012-3664-bf3b-6550d109d555"], "had4ab4e0g4df3g470bg859eg3274f721fb17": ["Run when they... shriek. They call... for others...", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "39e96830-06fd-80e3-afd6-c959fd4b7e15"], "h18d70724g6514g4236g8cfagf39a1dae3a6d": ["Did you have any valuables?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "fd4dcc24-57f4-cf5c-02d2-43883bd812f6"], "hc0052dc6gdcc0g4616gb34bg93fa5fa6a62d": ["Lihala's lute... where is... where...", "4a405fba-3000-4c63-97e5-a8001ebb883c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "91d872ff-ff0a-2482-5ce5-1718aa98b5f9"], "h8b11e394g83f7g45e6gbddfgcd836445a73d": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "15d255c1-1794-4355-814b-313b88d51dff"], "h41536835gcbf6g4f3fg9e3fge373af4476a8": ["*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SpeakWithDead\\DEN_TieflingBard_Dead.html", "e4c5f395-5a16-4965-b384-8da04f5ad243"]}